OL,3,CCouncil receive #5.3million in
OL,4,Csettlement with NEC over Bradford Live
OL,6,FThe original operator of a
OL,7,Fcontroversial #50million music venue
OL,8,Fin Bradford paid more than #5million
OL,9,Fto back out of its agreement with the
OL,10,Fcouncil, it has been revealed.
OL,12,FThe NEC Group had been due to run the
OL,13,F3,800-seater Bradford Live before it
OL,14,Fsuddenly announced it was pulling out
OL,15,Fin September 2024, four months before
OL,16,Fthe start of Bradford's year as UK
OL,17,FCity of Culture.
