OL,3,CCouncil receive #5.3million in
OL,4,Csettlement with NEC over Bradford Live
OL,6,FThe decision left Bradford Council
OL,7,Fsearching for a new operator for what
OL,8,Fwas hailed as the biggest regeneration
OL,9,Fscheme in the city centre.
OL,11,FTrafalgar Entertainment signed a 25-
OL,12,Fyear lease to manage the site in April.
OL,14,FIt has now been revealed NEC Group
OL,15,Fpaid #5.3million to Bradford Council
OL,16,Fafter it withdrew from its agreement.
