OL,3,CCouncil receive #5.3million in
OL,4,Csettlement with NEC over Bradford Live
OL,6,FCouncil leader Susan Hinchcliffe said:
OL,7,F"As people can see we secured a
OL,8,Fsignificant settlement from the NEC
OL,9,Fthat protected the interests of the
OL,10,FBradford district taxpayer.
OL,12,F"With the opening season for Bradford
OL,13,FLive under the fantastic new operator,
OL,14,FTrafalgar Entertainment, starting next
OL,15,Fmonth, we can now all look forward
OL,16,Fwith excitement to a wonderful future
OL,17,Ffor this amazing building."
