OL,3,CCouncil receive #5.3million in
OL,4,Csettlement with NEC over Bradford Live
OL,6,FBradford Live, on the site of the
OL,7,Fformer Odeon cinema, was initially
OL,8,Fforecast to cost between #22m and #25m
OL,9,Fand was due to open last year.
OL,11,FBut costs spiralled to #50m, with the
OL,12,Fcouncil putting in #44m, and the venue
OL,13,Fhas yet to open.
OL,15,FIt is now due hold its first gig on
OL,16,FYorkshire Day, 1 August.
